1037011.name: Voucher - Meido Next Door
1037011.desc:
Can be redeemed for Dark Mistletoe - Hodur's Outfit, Meido Next Door.
—A maid outfit improvised by Aether Gazer at the very last minute for the purposes of infiltration during a certain operation.
While the outfit felt a little odd when it was worn for the first time, it did what it was supposed to do, and quite beautifully at that.

1013011.name: Voucher - Flame Embers
1013011.desc:
Can be redeemed for Rāhu - Asura's Outfit, Flame Embers.
—Asura's everyday dress back in Shashvat, tailormade for her by Meruism in the local style.
The embers of Asura's flame will turn into battle scars and last forever.

1039011.name: Voucher - Blue Romance
1039011.desc:
Can be redeemed for Tidal Song - Poseidon's Outfit, Blue Romance.
—The blue-and-white colors and proper cut just spell leisure. An excellent casual look for the weekends.
One needs but a single glance to fall in love with the sea.

1148011.name: Voucher - School Days
1148011.desc:
Can be redeemed for Surefire - Zenkibo Tengu's Outfit, School Days.
—A design based on the high-school uniform look. Stay fresh and youthful on the battlefield with this look, yet still battle-ready.

1094021.name: Voucher - Butterfly Dreams
1094021.desc:
Can be used to redeem Darkstar - Hel's outfit, Butterfly Dreams.
—An exquisitely tailored cocktail dress inspired by a white butterfly that exists only in urban legends.
The phantom butterflies in the graveyard release a charming fragrance into the air as they flutter their wings, sending all in the vicinity into a dreamlike state where all worries have been cast aside for the moment...
1094021.desc_source: Limited-time sale in the Outfit Shop

1048011.name: Voucher - Sungleam
1048011.desc:
Can be used to redeem Comet R4Y - Zenkibo Tengu's everyday outfit, Sungleam.
—Made from a new type of reflective fabric developed by The Cryptics, this suit is capable of interfering with the enemy's vision and thus wins its wearer valuable time in battle.
According to a member of The Cryptics, Zenkibo has also quietly added a number of pockets to the outfit. Everyone knows why.

1066031.name: Voucher - Summer Blush
1066031.desc:
Can be used to redeem Early Sakura - Ookuninushi's outfit, Summer Blush.
—A swimsuit made out of technical fabric that Ookuninushi developed specially for the summer season. Stay cool and light as you enjoy the sun, sand, and sea.
It's just the blue skies, the warm breeze, the soothing waves, and you and me.

1093031.name: Voucher - Summer Lovin'
1093031.desc:
Can be used to redeem Jin-ei - Kuninotokotachi's outfit, Summer Lovin'.
—Kuninotokotachi's summer outfit of choice. Play a little game of peekaboo with the soft, drapey tulle material while retaining your ease of movement.
There is nothing better than watching the stars with your beloved on a beautiful summer night.

1058041.name: Voucher - Elegant Snooze
1058041.desc:
Can be used to redeem Ryugiri - Kagutsuchi's outfit, Elegant Snooze.
—A gift from a friend. This unique gown marries the classic Sephirah Zone style with design elements from Sasanami.
Kagutsuchi absolutely adores this outfit and wears it only on the most important occasions.

1042011.name: Voucher - Nighttime Iris
1042011.desc:
Can be used to redeem Puppet Master - Hades' outfit, Nighttime Iris.
—A gorgeous embroidered dress made by the premier dressmaker in Omorfies. Just like an iris in full bloom, every slight movement of the outfit releases an enchanting, yet dangerous, scent into the air.
Hades, who was personally involved in the design and production of the dress, showed a level of competence akin to a professional's throughout the process.

1199011.name: Voucher - Moonbeam Glimmer
1199011.desc:
Can be used to redeem Shinri - Tsukuyomi's outfit, Moonbeam Glimmer.
—Tsukuyomi asked for only one thing in her outfit: ease of movement. Despite receiving a clearly unsuitable outfit due to a logistics error, she accepted it silently as the personnel apologized repeatedly.
Perhaps she'll have a chance to wear it someday... maybe.

1032031.name: Voucher - Sonorous Tribute
1032031.desc:
Can be used to redeem AblaZe - Tyr's outfit, Sonorous Tribute.
A white formal attire made by the premier designer in the Omorfies Sephirah Zone, exquisitely designed and tailored to fit Tyr's temperament and figure perfectly.
Tyr treasures this outfit, which was a gift from someone very important to him.

1138011.name: Voucher - Bluesky Realm
1138011.desc:
Can be used to redeem Phantasmal Dawn - Hera's outfit, Bluesky Realm.
Hera herself provided the inspiration for this gown and was an active participant in its entire production process. When the finished product was ready, even the dressmaker couldn't help but admire Hera's profound understanding of herself and her beauty.
A blue bird soars through the majestic wilderness, as unfettered as Hera's artistic sensibilities in spite of the mundanity of this world.

1017011.name: Voucher - Disguise
1017011.desc:
Can be used to redeem Ailuros - Bastet's outfit, Disguise.
A garment backlogged in the corner of an Akkadian Guild warehouse. It's impossible to know for certain who originally ordered it. Bastet inadvertently turned it up when she was looking for a disguise for paying Jack of Hearts a visit.
It fits unexpectedly well.

1139031.name: Voucher - Lit by Glaciers
1139031.desc:
Can be used to redeem Arctic Abyss - Poseidon's formal wear, Lit by Glaciers.
—As her body begins to melt away in the sun, the ice bird still flutters toward the light on the horizon, yearning for its warm embrace.
Sing, not to mourn our parting, but to promise our reunion.
1139031.desc_source: Limited-time sale in the Outfit Shop

1111011.name: Voucher - Feathered Illusion
1111011.desc:
Can be used to redeem Living Soul - Osiris' formal wear, Feathered Illusion.
—Ausar's customized Gothic-style dress, featuring a light chiffon skirt with a black lining. Playful yet elegant.
She loves wearing it.
1111011.desc_source: Limited-time sale in the Outfit Shop

1028011.name: Voucher - Carol of Noise
1028011.desc:
Can exchange for Roaring Thunder - Thor's outfit "Carol of Noise".
—The first prize from a cider brewing celebration. Having drank too much herself, Thor sang all the way back to her dorm, unleashing electircity that almost caused the entire building's power system to fail.
1028011.desc_source: Limited-time sale in the Outfit Shop

1042041.name: Voucher - Lantern of Lethe
1042041.desc:
Can exchange for Puppet Master - Hades's outfit "Lantern of Lethe".
—A high-quality gown that displays Xu Heng District's finest craftsmanship, blending elegance and fashion while exuding dazzling radiance.
The ruler of the underworld crossed lethe, watching the vibrant lights of the mortal realm from across.
1042041.desc_source: Limited-time sale in the Outfit Shop

1039061.name: Voucher - The Drizzles
1039061.desc:
Can be used to redeem Tidal Song - Poseidon's outfit, "The Drizzles".
—Hand-crafted by a master tailor from a century-old store in Xu Heng District using classic styles and vintage patterns, resulting in a custom outfit that clings to a young lady's curves.
Little bridges, oil-paper umbrellas, morning drizzles, and a beauty among lotus blossoms.
1039061.desc_source: Limited-time sale in the Outfit Shop

1076011.name: Voucher - All Business
1076011.desc:
Can be used to redeem TaiYi - Gengchen's outfit: All Business.
—After receiving an unexpected request from Odin, Gengchen had no choice but to put on an Aether Gazer executive's suit and play the role of "Director" for a day.
1076011.desc_source: Limited-time sale in the Outfit Shop

1094041.name: Voucher - Symphonia Requiem
1094041.desc:
Can be used to redeem Darkstar - Hel's outfit: Symphonia Requiem.
—An elegant symphony orchestra suit made in the Omorfies style. Its exquisite tailoring is extremely figure-flattering.
The gates of the underworld open at midnight; the girl draws the butterflies, and the music begins.
1094041.desc_source: Limited-time sale in the Outfit Shop

1072011.name: Voucher - Miss Rice Dumpling
1072011.desc:
Can be used to redeem Omnisight - Luliang's outfit: Miss Rice Dumpling.
—Tian Lu Traders' first festival-themed outfit after its foray into the apparel industry, and it has adorable panda elements! Luliang even wore it herself on launch day to promote it.
Who in the world came up with this name anyway? It's a little on the nose, isn't it... Oh, you mean the boss lady came up with it herself? It's brilliant!
1072011.desc_source: Limited-time sale in the Outfit Shop

1041031.name: Voucher - Red and Black
1041031.desc:
Can be used to redeem Chord of Convallaria - Athena's outfit, Red and Black.
—An evening gown made for Athena by Artemis, said to be named after an ancient literary masterpiece. Exquisite dark patterns are embroidered onto the silk, and the skirt ripples like flowers in bloom.
A gown that's just as beautiful as you are.

106603.name: Summer Blush
106603.desc:
Early Sakura - Ookuninushi's outfit, Summer Blush.
—A swimsuit made out of technical fabric that Ookuninushi developed specially for the summer season. Stay cool and light as you enjoy the sun, sand, and sea.
It's just the blue skies, the warm breeze, the soothing waves, and you and me.

105804.name: Elegant Snooze
105804.desc:
Ryugiri - Kagutsuchi's outfit, Elegant Snooze.
—A gift from a friend. This unique gown marries the classic Sephirah Zone style with design elements from Sasanami.
Kagutsuchi absolutely adores this outfit and wears it only on the most important occasions.

104101.name: Knight of Gloria
104101.desc:
Chord of Convallaria - Athena's formal outfit, Knight of Gloria.
The outfit Athena wore when she took up her post as a Knight of Convallaria. It's both ornamental and combat-ready. In reality, however, Athena only wears it on solemn occasions.
The glory and faith of the Knights of Convallaria lives forever.

105201.name: Pioneer
105201.desc:
Rage Serpent - Marduk's outfit, Pioneer.
—The fifth-gen "Pioneer" metal armor. It perfectly fits the wearer's body structure and significantly increases their ability to fight solo.
This suit of armor carries a weighty, precious, and difficult-to-discuss past.

108403.name: Blossom in Snow
108403.desc:
New Pact - Verthandi's New Year outfit "Blossom in Snow".
—A creation from Xu Heng District's top designer. A uniquely-tailored spring festival outfit that makes Verthandi appear exceptionally adorable.
A faint scent of plum blossoms is still lingering on the fabric.

107401.name: Summer Breeze
107401.desc:
Winged Gardener - Yingzhao's outfit: Summer Breeze.
—A haute couture piece from a well-known tailor in Xu Heng. A comfortable swimwear that is a must-have for frequent travelers. Perfect for lounging on the beach!
Adequate rest is essencial for one to stay focused and productive.

107001.name: Under the Aqua Sky
107001.desc:
Tenblaze - Jinwu's outfit: Under the Aqua Sky.
—A gift from a good friend, Yingzhao. A haute couture piece from a well-known tailor in Xu Heng. Jinwu, a big fan of summertime, cannot express her love for this swimsuit more.
I-I... I'm not goofing off! It's just that I heard there are Yaoguai in the sea, too! I was just going to rehearse my moves, yeah, rehearse!

119904.name: After Class
119904.desc:
Shinri - Tsukuyomi's outfit, After Class.
—You receive a note tucked inside the pages of your textbook: the classmate who has always had excellent grades seems to have encountered some trouble, and is asking to speak to you alone after school... Is it something important?
"Admin, although this is just a photoshoot, what I'm going to say next... is serious."

109304.name: Personal Care Time
109304.desc:
Jin-ei - Kuninotokotachi's outfit, Personal Care Time.
—This is what Kuninotokotachi wears when she's delivering first aid lectures to the public for the Medical Center.
The faint smile she has when she looks at you suggests some sly plan in her mind.

105501.name: Rock Star
105501.desc:
So-ei - Kuramitsuha's outfit: Rock Star.
—The outfit Kuramitsuha wears when she's performing at an underground show. Both its tailoring and embellishments reflect a liveliness that is present in her music.
Move your body with abandon as the music flows through your veins: there is only the now.

107501.name: The Reanimated
107501.desc:
Untainted Heart - Lingguang's outfit, "The Reanimated."
—The healer's nimble silhouette weaves about a lonely old tomb. What has she found? A miracle cure lost to the ages, or a casualty in urgent need of medical attention?

104901.name: Higanbana
104901.desc:
Flower of Yomi - Izanami's outfit, "Higanbana."
—Izanami's ceremonial attire for Karasugo family festivals.
With her mother's help, young Izanami dons the spider lily and flame-patterned garment, not knowing that the word "death" would haunt her for the rest of her life.

113803.name: Dream of Thorned Roses
113803.desc:
Phantasmal Dawn - Hera's outfit "Dream of Thorned Roses."
—Hera wears this outfit for the Winter Festival dance. Its sharp cut contours her elegant figure.
And she is no doubt the most unforgettable stroke of burning red on the dance floor.

106101.name: Cloud and Mist
106101.desc:
A tailor was inspired to make this after strolling over Chang'an Bridge at night, and with it he sought to recreate how the moon looked reflected in the water.
She stands there, like a piece of flawless jade, like rustling willow leaves in spring. She stands there, dimming the colors of begonias and pear blossoms.

111102.name: Dragon Chant
111102.desc:
Clothes Ausar bought after reading the novel Osiris brought her from Xu Heng. She keeps it in her Imago Room.
"You traitors deserved to be burned in fire, struck by lightning and... Hey! Since when have you been standing there?!"

115001.name: SWAT Girl
115001.desc:
When fighting breaks out at the school, Buzenbo dresses up as a student so she can put a stop to it without the authorities getting involved.
"No matter what the task is, you gotta give it your all."

101501.name: Dangerous Training
101501.desc:
The uniform Sekhmet wore when she returned to her alma mater to work as a criminal psychology lecturer. It was probably around the time there were rumors on campus of a teacher who was "scarier than a serial killer."
"The only ones who arm themselves to the teeth are weak little children trying to look big. Now get a move on—it's time for class."

109501.name: Poem of Eventide
109501.desc:
The Admin's ball outfit was made by a celebrated Omorfies designer. Its simple cut belies its exquisite detailing.
"I can feel your heart beating fast. Mine is too, naturally."

107502.name: Yearning of a Dancing Sunset
107502.desc:
After finishing up business in Shashvat, the Admin shows an interest in the local dance. Lingguang can't turn down the rare chance to educate an outsider about their culture.
"I've learned some dances, but I'm in no way an expert... So, don't laugh at me."

107402.name: Efficiency First
107402.desc:
Tian Lu Traders always has much business to conduct, so the HR and Trade Director Yingzhao prizes efficiency above all else.
"What are you just standing there for? Don't you have anything better to do than stare at me?"

107601.name: All Business
107601.desc: After receiving an unexpected request from Odin, Gengchen had no choice but to put on an Aether Gazer executive's suit and play the role of "Director" for a day.

128401.name: Hymnal Fairy
128401.desc:
The uniform the girl was given after returning to Aether Gazer was the antithesis of the black armor that symbolizes fate—the clean white armor reminds her of the elven knight from her childhood books.
"Now... I really am the elven knight."

119701.name: Stardust
119701.desc:
The girl has bought herself a new outfit for her summer by the sea.
What dreams await her on the star-filled sea?

104902.name: Ocean's Love Song
104902.desc:
Wearing the dress that Izanami had given her for a previous invitation to the beach, the young lady had the figure of the legendary mermaid, and her deep, lustrous eyes seemed to hold the secrets of the deep sea.
"This is the first time I've seen such a striking sea view. Thank you, Questioner."

102201.name: Seaside Stroll
102201.desc:
Lightly dressed in vacation clothing, Selene had bought her outfit at a store on the island of Sylvester, only because it was the nearest store and the perfect size.
"Seaside strolling in a long dress tends to get the hemline dirty."

102101.name: Colorful Summer
102101.desc:
Before the young lady had become a commander, she would often play at the beach like any other girl. This time, to visit the beach with the Admin, she went and bought a brand new swimsuit.
"Oh, I didn't buy it just for this... My other swimsuit was just, uh, too old!"

104205.name: Lazy Vacation
104205.desc:
An exquisitely cut custom Omorfies swimsuit made out of super soft fabric, in one of the very few styles that has gained Hades's stamp of approval.
The summer flowers are blooming, and there is the sweet, sweet music from the sea waves.

102001.name: Veiled Dreams
102001.desc:
In order to spend a pleasant afternoon with the Admin, Brahmā used her powers to create a dressing gown for herself, designed and hand-cut by Brahmā herself.
"Always late, that Admin... So slow!"

106001.name: Gilded Edge
106001.desc:
Nine-Tailed Guardian - Luwu's "Gilded Edge" outfit.
—A beauty gifted me a blade of golden gleam. How might I requite such graciousness?
The winding road fills my heart with unease. Why do thoughts of it endlessly haunt me?

108901.name: Where Elegance Meets Extravagance
108901.desc: As Brahmā's deputy, Parvati always had some tasks she couldn't get away from, but fortunately... The Admin, her companion for tonight's dinner party, had put a little extra pep in her step to go and buy a new set of clothes for the date.

6004.name: Red Pavilion Whispers
6004.desc:
After returning from a visit to an old tomb, Lingguang hopes you can stay a little while longer.
—"You know... I'm only wearing this outfit for you. After tonight, it's going back in the closet... and it's staying there."

6005.name: See You Again
6005.desc:
After a fun day out, Zhiming seems somewhat reluctant to take you to the water's edge and fulfill the promise he just lost on the bet.
"Stay close to me... but not that close! Yes, that should be fine... Okay..."

6006.name: Untouchable
6006.desc:
It's the trill of the phoenix flute, the shadows of the lanterns, your laughter as it rings out above the hustle and bustle of the city.
"I'm just tired—it feels like you've been dragging me around all day. What is it you're expecting, exactly?"

6007.name: Courtyard Echoes
6007.desc: The afternoon sun, tipsy wind, and intoxicating fragrance of flowers. This piece is an unforgettable and poignant commemoration of us.

6008.name: Have A Dance With Me?
6008.desc: This dance is just for you, Admin. The figure is graceful and smells faintly of orchids. It's hard to ascertain whether this is a moment of serenity, or just all a dream.

6009.name: Time to Relax
6009.desc: The chance encounter in the elevator has shown people a different side to Gengchen. Maybe tailor-made clothes are never as good as we want them to be?

6010.name: Moment of Panic
6010.desc: I'm always very organized with work, but for some reason I always make mistakes whenever you're nearby. I didn't know you panicked like that too.

6011.name: Sleepwalker
6011.desc: As night falls, Admin comes across a girl immersed in a sweet dream. In the silent twilight, the only thing that moves is time.

6012.name: That First Glimmer of Light
6012.desc: Never-seen-before landscapes, unfamiliar shores... It's all a bit overwhelming for a young lady. What's Admin up to this time?

6013.name: Gentle Echo
6013.desc:
It's a scene Poseidon has always loved, and you're the only one she wants to share it with.
Let's turn that summer into the best of memories.

6014.name: Amid Moonlight
6014.desc: As the evening breeze wafted through Selene's hair, this small world felt calm and quiet yet bursting with meaning. The waves were as gentle as the moonlit sky, while the moon seemed to be gazing back at her.

6015.name: Maiden's Daydream
6015.desc: The young lady had purchased a drink to pass the time waiting for the Admin to get back, but for some reason, whenever she was with the Admin, the pace of her steps always seemed to get disrupted...

6016.name: Afternoon Delight
6016.desc: That afternoon in the room, were Brahmā's sudden words true or false? Unfortunately, she's the only one who knows the answer.

6021.name: When the City Lights Up
6021.desc: After the clamor of dinner was done, the two enjoyed the remainder of the night. That was the time for Parvati to really relax.
